headline: Sovos Launches Global Partnership with Intuit to Deliver Best-in-Class E-Invoicing for Intuit Users
summary: ATLANTA, August 19, 2025--Sovos, the always-on compliance company, today announced a global strategic partnership that will bring Sovos’ market-leading e-invoicing capabilities to Intuit customers, starting with QuickBooks. headline: ImagineX Named to 2025 Inc. 5000 List of America's Fastest-Growing Private Companies
summary: Inc. today announced that ImagineX has been named to the 2025 Inc. 5000 list, the annual ranking of the fastest-growing private companies in America. This marks ImagineX's third time earning a spot on the list, following previous honors in 2020 and 2021.
